product_name: Bowmore 10 Year Old Single Malt 1L
description:
An unapologetically bold fusion of flavours. Spanish oak sherry casks add a
spicy twist to our signature peat smoke, creating a marriage of fire and earth.
A diverse spectrum of aromas start with citrus and progress to smoked peat
and walnuts.
Islay whiskies are famed for their peaty smokiness.  Bowmore, the third bestselling
Islay, is certainly no exception. With a nose of sun-dried fruit, baked
Seville orange and toasted maple, it’s no wonder its dark amber in colour, or
has a palette of sultanas, sea-salt and dark fruit oils. When you uncork a bottle
of the 10 year old, you open the door to deeper character and flavour. 40% Alcohol

product_name: Brookie's Byron Slow Gin 700ml
description: Brookie’s Byron Slow Gin is the first of its kind. Made in the traditional style of the English ‘Sloe’ gin, Brookie’s Byron Slow Gin showcases a unique rainforest fruit native to the subtropical region of Byron Bay, the Davidson Plum. We steep these plums in our Byron Dry Gin and let time weave its magic. Expect exhilarating flavours of rose, watermelon, and bright plum.

product_name: Mac By Brookie's 700ml
description: Mac. by Brookie’s is a premium roasted Macadamia & Wattleseed liqueur. Crafted with natural ingredients, Mac. was made to shake things up! A versatile little nutter made from locally sourced roasted Macadamia Nuts & toasted Native Australian Wattleseed. The end result is the ‘Mac Daddy’ of all nut liqueurs. Effortlessly smooth, Mac. fits into any social occasion. Pour over ice with a slice of lime AKA the Easy Mac. , or mix into your Espresso Martini for something a little more unexpected. Brought to you by Brookie’s, you can rest assure that Mac. captures the true spirit of Byron.

product_name: Brookie's Turkish Delight Gin 700ml
description: Loud in colour, yet delicate and balanced in flavour Brookie's Turkish Delight Gin is a celebration of the friendship between Brookie’s Gin and The Smoking Camel. Brookie’s x The Smoking Camel Turkish Delight Gin is made by infusing Brookie’s Gin with the perfect balance of fragrant rose, orange blossom, delicate meyer lemon and balanced with a touch of sweetness. The gin was created with the help of Eddie Brook’s mum Pam Brook, who says ‘Brookie’s Turkish Delight was made not from the flavours of modern day commercial Turkish delight, but from my memories of tastes and smells in exotic Turkish sweet shops which abounded in inner Melbourne'. Alcohol:  38%

product_name: Bulldog London Dry Gin 1L
description: Bulldog is a modern reinterpretation of London Dry Gin, wisely created with exotic botanicals making it unexpectedly smooth. Its 12 botanicals include White Poppy from Turkey, along with Dragon Eye and Lotus Leaf from China; adding a layer of distinction to its refreshing citrus notes. Founded in the USA by a daring entrepreneur with the ambition to create the first modern Gin. This is the birthplace of Bulldog. Enjoy Bulldog Responsibly. Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Bundaberg Small Batch Rum 700ml
description: Hand crafted by blending the finest Bundaberg Rums with the richest aged reserves matured in Brandy & Cognac Barrels for a sweet and smooth finish. Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Bundaberg Up Rum Twin Pack 2 X 1.125L
description: First distilled in 1888, Bundaberg is Australia's own rum. It's made from 100% Queensland sugar cane which shows through with flavours of molasses and caramel. Best drunk with cola on ice, and a couple of good mates.  Tasting notes:Fresh and dry timber notes and a prickling pepper heat that rounds off to dark caramel undertones. 37% Alcohol

product_name: Bundaberg Red Rum 1L
description: Bundaberg Red has been crafted to deliver an incredibly smooth taste while retaining the unique character for which Bundaberg Rum is famous. Filtered through red gum charcoal to deliver an incredibly smooth finish with hints of brown sugar, caramel and honey. It goes perfectly with cola, over ice and with a wedge of lime.  Tasting notes:Silky notes of vanilla custard and buttered toffee candies, with a herbaceous freshness and light, smooth mouthfeel. 37% Alcohol

product_name: Bundaberg UP Rum 1.125L
description: First distilled in 1888, Bundaberg is Australia's own rum. It's made from 100% Queensland sugar cane which shows through with flavours of molasses and caramel. Best drunk with cola on ice, and a couple of good mates.  Tasting notes: Fresh and dry timber notes and a prickling pepper heat that rounds off to dark caramel undertones. 37% Alcohol

product_name: Bundaberg Op Rum 1.125L
description: First distilled in 1888, Bundaberg Rum is as Australian as it gets. Made from 100% sugar cane then matured to perfection, Bundaberg Rum Overproof is distilled and aged for a bold, rich flavour full of oak, caramel and spice. Tasting notes:Sweet, ripe pineapple and dark brown sugar that leads to oily leather and drying herbal tones. Alcohol:  57.7%

product_name: Burberry Mr. Burberry Eau De Toilette 100ml
description: Introducing Mr. Burberry. Classic yet contemporary; sophisticated and sensual. The signature Eau de Toilette captures the essence of London and its moments, fusing classic scents of British perfumery with unexpected ingredients.

product_name: Burberry Goddess Eau De Parfum Intense 100ml
description: The Burberry Goddess Eau de Parfum Intense campaign continues to follow Emma Mackey and a pride of lionesses on their journey of self-discovery. With renewed strength and confidence, Emma embodies the spirit of Burberry Goddess. As the sun sets, she draws strength from its rays and releases the power within. This Burberry fragrance is a gourmand aromatic woody scent. The signature trio of vanillas from Goddess Eau de Parfum is amplified with a fourth vanilla wood (vanilla SFE), that has a smoky character. When combined with luminous lavender essence, it intensifies the fragrance with a vibrant woody scent. Inspired by the colours at sunset, Burberry Goddess Eau de Parfum Intense is housed in a square bottle filled with a light ambery fragrance and decorated with a golden medallion. Dark beige packaging with a gabardine-inspired gold label references the brand’s heritage. Burberry Goddess Eau de Parfum Intense is designed to be refilled. Refill sold separately.

product_name: Burberry Her Garden Party Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: Burberry Her Eau de Toilette for women, is a floral fruity fragrance for women. A blooming peony fragrance, blended with joyful and juicy green pear top notes enhanced with honeysuckle and rose, softened by an addictive woody base.

product_name: Burberry Her Elixir Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Burberry Her Elixir de Parfum: a bold and sensual fragrance for women. Moving beyond the adventurous spirit of the Burberry Her Eau de Parfum, the scent is the latest chapter in the intensifying story of Burberry Her. Designed for women who dare to explore the unknown, this Burberry scent is for the free-spirited woman seeking the excitement of her next adventure. Sensual, irresistible and not held back by boundaries, she possesses an addictive persona. An intense addition to the Burberry Her family, this enticing perfume for women offers signature fruity gourmand notes alongside a daring burst of dark red berries with jasmine, rounded with the sensual and addictive fragrance of vanilla and amber. Burberry Her Elixir de Parfum deepens the pink of the Eau de Parfum bottle, transforming it into an opaque finish representing the intensity of the fragrance inside and its confident and sensual nature. The outer design of this perfume bottle features raised Burberry lettering at the base.

product_name: Burberry Hero Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: Burberry Hero Eau de Parfum portrays a modern man. Sincere yet courageous, he constantly surpasses himself in every challenge. No longer held back by preconceptions, he connects with his inner self to embrace the extraordinary within. Burberry Hero men's Eau de Parfum. The powerful scent of a forest growing by the English coastline. Pine needles blended with benzoin and incense with a trio of warm cedarwood oils at the base. Housed in a refillable, deep oak-coloured bottle and finished with gold hues. Refill sold separately. Intense and invigorating. Burberry Hero Eau de Parfum for men. The perfume bottle is refillable thanks to an innovative and sustainable refill system. A vegan perfume for any occasion.

product_name: Calvin Klein Eternity Eau De Parfum For Her 100ml
description: Eternity for Women is a contemporary floral fragrance. Inspired by modern romance, this Eau de Toilette embodies a timeless elegance. Top notes of bergamot, white lily, and white rose finish with spicy tones of sandalwood.

product_name: Burberry Hero Parfum 50ml
description: Burberry Hero Parfum portrays a modern man. Sincere yet courageous, he constantly surpasses himself in every challenge. No longer held back by preconceptions, he connects with his inner self to embrace the extraordinary within. Hero Parfum is the latest Burberry fragrance for men. Intense and powerful, the scent is led by a base of warm cedarwood oils. On top, notes of Amyris and Cypriol oil enliven the aroma for a deep woody finish. Housed in an angular glass bottle detailed with the Burberry logo. Intense and powerful, Burberry Hero Parfum. A vegan parfum for any occasion. How to use:  Spray Burberry Hero Parfum on to your pulse points, focusing on your neck, behind your ears, and your chest to give the scent the warmth it needs to intensify.

product_name: Burberry Her Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: Her Eau de Toilette for women, the free-spirited Burberry scent. A gourmand fragrance balancing joyful fruity notes over an addictive drydown. For the bold modern woman who loves adventure. Her Eau de Toilette for women is a playful blend of blooming peony, joyful green pear top notes, strawberry, blackcurrant and pink peppercorn. Enhanced with a honeysuckle heart, lily of the valley and rose, the fruity floral scent is softened by an addictive musk and cedarwood base. With the powerfully feminine Eau de Toilette comes the new face of Burberry Her: Fran Summers. As she explores the city, Fran's captivating energy, confidence and effortless individuality embody the essence of the modern Burberry woman. Entranced, she sees her world from a new perspective. A break from expectation. A new discovery. Tradition meets modernity in the understated glass design of the Her Eau de Toilette perfume bottle. Refreshed in pistachio green with the matching iconic ribbon, the design captures the spontaneous and spirited nature of the Burberry scent.

product_name: Burberry Hero Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Notes of fragrant incense and benzoin on an earthy base of cedarwood oils and pine. Housed in a deep oak-coloured bottle, finished with gold hues. Intense and invigorating.

product_name: Burberry Hero Eau De Toilette 100ml
description: A trio of cedarwood oils, invigorated by juniper and black pepper, brightened with bergamot. Housed in an angular glass bottle engraved with the Burberry logo. Strength and subtlety.

product_name: Burberry Hero Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: A trio of cedarwood oils, invigorated by juniper and black pepper, brightened with bergamot. Housed in an angular glass bottle engraved with the Burberry logo. Strength and subtlety.

product_name: Calvin Klein Ck Everyone Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: Clean. Green. Citrus. CK EVERYONE is a genderless scent for today that celebrates the infinite freedom of self-expression. Vegan, with organic orange oil and housed in a recyclable glass bottle.

product_name: Calvin Klein Eternity Eau De Parfum For Him 50ml
description: Refined and sophisticated, ETERNITY Calvin Klein Eau de Parfum celebrates the concepts of modern masculinity. A new woody note reinvents the original fougère scent, providing crisp freshness with a powerful yet elegant trail.

product_name: Calvin Klein Ck Everyone Eau De Toilette 100ml
description: Clean. Green. Citrus. CK EVERYONE is a genderless scent for today that celebrates the infinite freedom of self-expression. Vegan, with organic orange oil and housed in a recyclable glass bottle.

description: Refined and sophisticated, ETERNITY Calvin Klein Eau de Parfum celebrates the concepts of modern masculinity. A new woody note reinvents the original fougère scent, providing crisp freshness with a powerful yet elegant trail.

product_name: Calvin Klein Deep Euphoria Fresh Eau De Toilette 50ml
description:
Liberated – empowered – provocative 
deep euphoria enters a new olfactive territory as the first vibrant chypre floral in the calvin klein portfolio. 
the fragrance opens with notes of cascalone and black magic rose that intertwine to create an aura of humidity throughout the entire fragrance, imparting a sultry wetness that enhances the signature sensuality. the top and mid’s mix brings a modern femininity and a pure quality of richness to the fragrance, and the drydown of enveloping sensual musk brings a smooth, sensual texture that is rich and undeniably sensual, immersing you deep within the fragrance, evoking warmth and pleasure.
these complementary elements embody a unique dichotomy of empowerment and true glamour, expressing the many facets of the deep euphoria woman’s personality.

product_name: CALVIN KLEIN CK ALL Eau de Toilette 50ml
description: CK All redefines freedom from societal conventions. One fragrance for all, recognizing individuality. Frozen mandarin and grapefruit flower are layered with warm musk and amber notes for a lingering warm finish.

product_name: Calvin Klein Ck One Gold Eau De Toilette 100ml
description: A bold and unapologetic fragrance that radiates warmth and commands attention.  The fragrance carries notes of fig, layered with bright neroli and vibrant, sensual vetiver.

product_name: Calvin Klein Defy Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Fresh. Courageous. Seductive. Calvin Klein Defy Eau de Parfum is a provocative new Calvin Klein perfume for the daring modern man. Defiant of boundaries and expectations, the premium CK scent builds upon the original signature woody base with an unexpected darker, warmer twist. Opening with crisp top notes of mandarin oil and black pepper, this Calvin Klein scent has an irresistible fresh burst. Addictive and intense, the heart of velvety smooth leather accord offers a deep contrast to the freshness of the top notes, incorporating saffiano and rich suede in a new, rugged way. The base of vetiver oil – responsibly sourced from Haiti – anchors the vigor of this citrus perfume, adding strength, naturality and purpose to the aroma with a lasting masculine signature. Encapsulating the very essence of the Calvin Klein man, this uniquely rich Calvin Klein scent is housed in a unique bottle evoking denim and the iconic codes of CK’s iconic minimalism. The opposing straight corners and round curves of the silhouette pair to represent both sides of this defiant and confident man, vulnerability and courage, dueling components that join to tell a complex story.

product_name: Calvin Klein Defy Eau De Toilette 100ml
description:
Fresh. Masculine. Addictive. 
 Calvin Klein Defy is a daring contrast of invigorating freshness and powerful woods. For the modern man who breaks boundaries while exploring his authentic truths and the contrasts within. 
 The scent opens with an addictive citrus blend highlighting crisp Bergamot and fresh Lavender Absolute. Rugged and earthy Vetiver Oil—responsibly sourced from Haiti—is the heart of the fragrance, connecting the vibrant textural elements with a rich and alluring base of Amber notes. 
 Packaged in a modern bottle that reflects the iconic codes of Calvin Klein—denim blues and minimalism infused with a sensual edge. It has a textured matte cap atop the curved yet sharp silhouette, representing the duality of vulnerability and courage on the path to defiance. 
 Dare to Defy.

product_name: Canadian Club Classic 12YO 1L
description: Considered one of Canadian Clubs premium offerings, this whiskey is one that can be enjoyed on its own, or in your favourite mixes. Aged 12 years in American white oak it shows their trademark smoothness and a long, dry finish. With the long ageing process the whiskey has developed dark tones and the traditional characteristics of aged whiskies being rich and strong aromatics.  Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Canadian Club 1L
description: The one that started the legend! Like all our whiskies 1858 Original is blended before ageing. This allows the subtle flavours of the rye, rye malt, barley and corn to marry perfectly before their long sleep in top quality white oak barrels. The result is a smooth, light, mellow flavour that is the first choice of millions in over 156 countries around the World.  Alcohol:  37%

product_name: Captain Morgan Original Spiced Gold Rum 1L
description: The original. The icon. It’s Captain Morgan Original Spiced Gold Rum, flavoured with the taste of vanilla, other natural flavours and spice for an irresistibly sweet yet subtly spiced taste. Versatility is its speciality. Make it hot, make it cold, make it sweet, make it fruity or even make it creamy. Delicious possibilities are there for the making.

product_name: Caol Ila 12 Year Old Single Malt Scotch Whisky 1.0 Litre 43%
description: Nestled in a hidden cove near Port Askaig, Islay, the Caol Ila (pronounced “Cull Eela”) distillery sent its whisky to market by sea for over a hundred years. Caol Ila is the Gaelic name for the Sound of Islay, which separates the island from Jura in one of the most remote and beautiful parts of Scotland's West Coast. The distillery was founded in 1846 and is situated on the shores of the Sound, a spot originally chosen partly because of the clean water from Loch Nam Ban which still provides its main supply. Fresh, sweetly fruity and smooth-bodied, Caol Ila 12 year old is the colour of pale straw, with a delicate balance of tastes. The clean, appetising nose shows subtle citrus fruit with just a puff of smoke. Firm and smooth, it begins sweetly then yields a fragrant smokiness and a sweet-smoky, lingering finish. This single malt was named Outstanding Silver Medal Winner at the International Wine & Spirits Competition 2015. The ultimate Islay malt, Caol Ila is considered by experts to be the perfect entry point into the world of peaty malt whiskies and a reference for connoisseurs of Islay Single Malt Scotch Whisky the world over. Tasting notes:Peaty, yet fresh and smooth, lightly fragranced with olive oil notes

product_name: Bushmills Black Rush 80/20 1L
description: Colour:  Amber gold Nose:  Big, bold aromas of rich fruitcake and the intense sherry sweetness characteristic of Pedro Ximénez sherry casks. Taste:  Soft and silky mouthfeel with a distinctive toasted nut character, hints of allspice and a punch of ripe peaches. Finish:  The intricate marriage of smooth triple distilled spirit with PX sherry cask complexity results in layers of flavour, and a long and lingering finish. Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Bushmills 10Yo Sherry Cask 1L
description: Celebrating over four decades of collaboration with Spain's finest sherry cask makers, the Paez family, we created this 10 year old single malt whiskey, aged for a minimum of 10 years in bourbon and sherry casks, married and finished in aromatic oloroso sherry butts from the Paez-Morilla bodega, Jerez, Spain. The result: The honeyed maltiness of the regular Bushmills 10 year old is intensified in this darker flavoured liquid, available only in Global travel retail. Tasting Notes: Nose: Oaky vanilla, alongside sticky apricot compote, and spicy fruit cake. Palate: Sherry sweetness, with sun dried raisins, warm clove, and a touch of toasted marzipan. Finish: Baking spices, with the fruitcake lingering. Alcohol:  46%

product_name: Carolina Herrera Bad Boy Eau De Toilette 50ml
description:
BAD BOY is a fragrant expression of duality, representing the bold nature and alluring complexity of the modern man. At once strong and sensitive, confident and relaxed, BAD BOY embraces his contrasting characteristics with a strikingly assured ease. A scent of distinct sophistication that continues to intrigue, inspired by the man who wears it.  
 
 Ingredients:  PARFUM (FRAGRANCE), AQUA (WATER), COUMARIN, ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, LINALOOL, LIMONENE, ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, GERANIOL, CITRAL, CITRONELLOL, METHYL 2-OCTYNOATE, HYDROXYCITRONELLAL, CINNAMAL.

Intensely seductive, Good Girl EDP Supreme reinvents the iconic Good Girl fragrance with a daring new formula. product_name: Carolina Herrera Bad Boy Cobalt Elixir Eau De Parfum 100ml

A bold blend of dark and light elements for the woman of contrast, Good Girl Gold Fantasy Eau de Parfum is a daring yet sophisticated fragrance inspired by Carolina Herrera's unique vision of the duality of the modern woman. She defies expectations: at once bold and alluring, elegant and modern, kind and mysterious.

product_name: Bruichladdich Laddie 8 700ml
description: The 'New make' spirit sets out on its journey through life full of the crisp, fresh, malty flavours derived from trickle distillation - but it is careful management of American and European oak casks that eventually determines the final character of the whisky. Adam’s aim with this vatting is to preserve the elegant, floral notes of the vibrant young spirit while building up the signature salty, citrus tang so characteristic of Bruichladdich. Eight years maturation in Bruichladdich's warehouses on the shores of Loch Indaal have perfected a graceful single malt that relates to a very modern craftsmanship

product_name: Carolina Herrera Very Good Girl Eau De Parfum 80ml
description:
Fabulous and fearless, Very Good Girl is a bold new interpretation of the iconic Good Girl scent that will walk straight into your heart with its seductive rose scent and red-hot design. Evolving Carolina Herrera's vision of the duality of the modern woman, this sumptuous and surprising Eau de Parfum shows us that the multifaceted nature of contemporary femininity is where the true beauty of being a woman lies.  
 
 Ingredients:  ALCOHOL DENAT., PARFUM (FRAGRANCE), AQUA (WATER), LINALOOL, LIMONENE, COUMARIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, CITRAL, ISOEUGENOL, GERANIOL, CI 14700 (RED 4), CI 60730 (EXT. VIOLET 2).

product_name: Carolina Herrera Bad Boy Le Parfum Eau De Parfum 100ml

BAD BOY Le Parfum redefines the iconic BAD BOY scent with an electrifying new formula that’s bolder than ever before. Unapologetic, authentic and mysterious, this irreverent scent embodies the duality of modern man with a surprising blend of high-voltage hemp and warm, seductive leather. product_name: Celebrations Pouch 450g
description: Launched in 1997, Celebrations was the first to bring together a selection of well-loved brands in miniature. With a mix of everyone's favourites, Celebrations is a guaranteed crowd-pleaser for any occasion. Ingredients:  Sugar, glucose syrup, cocoa butter, skimmed milk powder, cocoa mass, peanuts, milk fat, desiccated coconut, lactose, whey powder (from milk), sunflower oil, whole milk powder, palm fat, emulsifiers (soya lecithin, mono- and diglycerides of fatty acids), skimmed condensed milk, barley malt extract, reduced-fat cocoa, salt, humectant (glycerol), egg white powder, wheat flour, natural vanilla extract, coconut oil, hydrolysed milk protein, raising agents (monocalcium phosphate, sodium hydrogen carbonate, potassium hydrogen carbonate, tricalcium phosphate). Allergens:  Contains milk, peanuts, soya, gluten (wheat, barley), egg Warnings:  May contain hazelnuts.

product_name: Chalk Hill Barbera 750ml
description: A perfumed wine with perfumed rose petals, dark cherry and spice. A medium bodied wine with bright cherry and red currant fruits on the front palate. It has a firm line of acid and finishes with lingering spice notes. The perfect match with umami-rich food . This wine drinks well young, but will be at its peak in 5-7 years. FOOD MATCH: Chickpea pancakes with rainbow chard and spicy lamb. Alcohol:  14%

product_name: Chalk Hill Chardonnay 750ml
description: Aromatic nose of citrus and nectarine fruits, complimented with jasmine florals hints ginger and a background of shortbread. A well-structured wine with a refined edge. The palate shows fruits of white nectarine and pear. It is textured, with shortbread, spice and hints of roasted hazelnut, finishing dry with a good acid line and minerality. Enjoy now to 2026. FOOD MATCH: Smoked Chicken, Camembert and Spinach Salad. Alcohol:  13%

product_name: Chalk Hill Tempranillo Grenache 750ml
description: Red berries, aromatic floral nose, Turkish delight and hints of red licorice mix with earthy leathery spice and background pepper. The palate is medium weighted showing a mix of fresh berry fruits- raspberry, mulberry and pomegranate, along with warm spice and dried herbs. The wine has a vibrant acidity and a lovely line of fine minerally tannin. This wine drinks well young, but will cellar for 5-7 years. FOOD MATCH: Honey Bang Bang's Lamb Cutlets. Alcohol:  14.5%

product_name: Chalk Hill Syrah 750ml
description: A vibrant nose of florals, dark cherry, spice and red strap licorice notes. This is a medium bodied shiraz with dark cherry fruit combining with blueberries and mulberry notes. It has a lovely textured palate with a lingering finish with spice notes and cocoa. This wine drinks well young, but will be at its peak in 5-7 years. FOOD MATCH: Ricotta and Spinach Cannelloni Alcohol:  14.5%

product_name: Chalk Hill Poetica Moscato 750ml
description: Wine opens with lifted and abundant tropical fruit with floral notes - think Lychee fruit and peach iced tea. A slight spritz on the palate provides an effervescent burst of bright tropical fruit. Nice crisp acid finishes off the luscious fruit driven palate. Now to 2 years. FOOD MATCH: Lemon Meringue Pie. Alcohol:  6.5%

product_name: Chalk Hill Luna Cabernet Sauvignon 750ml
description: Opaque black dark red colour with a dark red hue. Aromas of mulberries and dark cherries merge with cedary tobacco and spicy dried herb notes. The palate has good body weight and richness whilst still retaining a cool climate elegance. It features flavours of dark mulberries and ripe dark cherries infused with tobacco over a spicy cedar background. Fine grained tannins provide a solid structure with an aftertaste of mulberries, ripe dark cherries, cedary tobacco characters and spice. Alcohol:  14%

product_name: Chalk Hill Europa Chardonnay 750ml
description: AROMA: A delightful nose of citrus, pear and melon fruits, with a hint of whipped cream and cashews. TASTE: The palate is bright and fresh with white stone fruit bursting onto the front palate. It is offset by a crisp, minerally dry finish. Alcohol:  13%

product_name: Canadian Club 200ml
description: The one that started the legend! Like all our whiskies 1858 Original is blended before ageing. This allows the subtle flavours of the rye, rye malt, barley and corn to marry perfectly before their long sleep in top quality white oak barrels. The result is a smooth, light, mellow flavour that is the first choice of millions in over 156 countries around the World. 37% Alc./Vol.

product_name: Chambord Black 700ml
description: Chambord is the premium black raspberry liqueur with a fine French heritage. Chambord stands alone in its category and in its iconic, captivating packaging. For the person who appreciates a life full of great experiences, Chambord is the essential spirit that elevates and brings magic to cocktailing and culinary experiences. Captivating to the most discerning palate, Chambord tempts and rewards experimentation.  16.5% Alc./Vol.

product_name: Chandon Nv Brut 750ml
description: Chandon non vintage brut is a classic australian sparkling. well loved and a firm favourite by those who love a bit of bubble in their glass. quality has always been a constant with chandon brut and has become a benchmark for every other australian sparkling to aspire to. fresh and vibrant. Alcohol: 13%

product_name: Chateau Tanunda 100Yo Vines Shiraz 750ml
description: The wine delivers classic regional characters of dense, spicy blueberry fruit and savoury pan jus. Hints of liquorice, plum, and all-spice all delicately interwoven. A fine grained tannin structure and depth of favour all show that this wine has incredible future ahead of it. Alcohol:  14.9%

product_name: Chateau Tanunda Single Vineyard Grenache 750ml
description: A full bodied wine with aromas of blackberry, plum and white pepper supported by spicy, dark berry fruits and rich dark chocolate on the palate. The extensive finish is framed by elegant, fine-grained tannins. Alcohol:  14.5%

product_name: Chateau Tanunda Tawny 500ml
description: This tawny shows intense flavours of raisins, prunes, orange peel cinnamon and nutty complexity with a long clean finish. Presented in its own individual gift box, it is a must for all lovers of Barossa fortified. Alcohol:  18%

product_name: Chateau Tanunda Grand Barossa Shiraz 750ml
description: Grand Barossa Shiraz epitomises the premium international reputation for Shiraz which has made the Barossa Valley famous. Lifted aromas of blackberry, plum and black pepper are accompanied by spicy, dark berry fruits on the palate. Alcohol:  15%

product_name: Ciroc Red Berry Vodka 1L
description: An exceptionally smooth vodka having been distilled 5 times and unlike most vodkas that are distilled from grain. CIROC is crafted from fresh succulent grapes.    40% Alc./Vol.

product_name: Chupa Chups Backpacks 192g
description: The soft toy contains a variety of 16 fruit flavoured Chupa Chups lollipops and can be re-used as a fun backpack, making it a perfect gift item for kids.

product_name: Ciroc Premium Vodka 200ml
description:
Ciroc is one of the only vodkas in the world made from fine French grapes
Ciroc has won double gold at the 2010 San Francisco World Spirits Competition
Ciroc vodka has an exceptionally smooth and delicious citrus taste
Ciroc can be enjoyed in a Ciroc Blue Stone long drink
40ml Ciroc, 20ml Lemon Juice, 10ml Vanilla Syrup, topped with soda
Ciroc is the perfect gift to bring to the chicest at home celebrations Tasting notes:Made from fine French grapes, our  CiROC snap frost vodka has a characteristically smooth and clean profile.  40% Alcohol

product_name: Chivas Regal The Chivas Brothers' Blend Scotch Whisky 1L
description: Created as a tribute to the Chivas Brothers and their legendary blending skills, this 12-year old blend uses a carefully selected range of malt whiskies, including higher proportions of Strathisla and Longmorn Single Malts, in order to recreate the extra smooth taste that made their whiskies famous. The Chivas Brothers’ Blend is an ultra-smooth and easy drinking whisky, perfect for sharing with friends. Tasting Notes: Colour: Rich amber Nose: Bursting with ripe, soft fruit flavours, including peach and pear, and accented with runny honey, marmalade and soft candy Taste: Rich taste of fresh soft fruit flavours, echoing the nose, giving way to a fantastic sweet, creamy texture Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Chivas Regal 18 Yo Scotch Whisky 1L
description:
Chivas 18 is a uniquely rich and multi-layered whisky, meticulously blended by Master Blender Colin Scott. With 85 unique flavour notes in every drop, every taste is a new experience
 Colour:  Intense, dark amber Nose:  Rich, indulgent, multi-layered aromas with hints of dried fruits, buttery toffee and dark chocolate Taste:  A velvety, dark chocolate palate yields to elegant floral notes and a wisp of sweet, mellow smokiness Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Chivas Regal 12 Yo Scotch Whisky 1L
description:
Chivas is a blend of many different malt and grain Scotch whiskies, matured for at least 12 years. This rich, smooth blend balances style with substance and tradition with a modern twist.
 Colour:  Radiant, warm amber Nose:  An aromatic infusion of wild herbs, heather, honey and orchard fruits Taste:  Round and creamy with a full, rich taste of honey and ripe pears, with vanilla, hazelnut and butterscotch notes Alcohol:  40%

product_name: Chivas Extra Regal 13 Year Old Sherry Cask 1L
description: Chivas Regal Extra Sherry Cask is bursting with the rich fruity aromas of ripe pears and melons, then comes the subtle sweetness of both creamy toffee and milk chocolate to fill your senses. Rich deep flavours of sweet ripe pears in syrup balanced with the luxurious taste of vanilla caramels and cinnamon sweets. The tantalising finish is full of spicy notes of cinnamon and ginger which dance around in the background overlaid with hints of a sweet Sherry nuttiness.

product_name: Chivas Extra 13 Year Old Rum Cask Blended Scotch Whisky 1L
description: This Chivas Extra 13 Blended Scotch Whisky selectively finished* in Rum Cask is inspired by the Chivas brothers’ 13 King Street Emporium in Aberdeen, where they imported different spirits, exotic spices, and luxury food items from across the globe. Imparting its own unique combination of characteristics onto the Chivas blend, this finish brings new and contrasting flavour notes to the spirit for the first time.

product_name: Chivas Regal Extra 13 Year Bourbon Cask Blended Scotch Whisky 1L
description: This splendid 13 year old blended Scotch whisky joins the Chivas Regal range, and a selection of the whisky that goes into the blend is matured in bourbon casks. The result is a bright and creamy profile, with sweet oak and vanilla shining through. Great for sipping and should be ideal for mixing up some tasty cocktails. Alcohol:  40% Taste:  Nose: Vanilla and oak are there right away, followed by a touch of orange zest and melted butter. Palate: Sweet vanilla caramel, buttered popcorn, pressed apples and mellow spice. Finish: Gently peppery warmth builds, with plenty of creamy malt, tangy oak, and smooth spice.

product_name: Chivas Regal 12YO Blended Scotch Whisky 200ml
description: Savour the excellence of Chivas Regal 12 Year Old in the convenient 200mL size at Red Bottle! Elevate your next Whisky experience with the timeless charm of Chivas Regal – order now for a taste of Scottish heritage. Alcohol:  40%

Finally, a vibrant cedarwood from Virginia meets a sensual vanilla from Madagascar and white musks to sign the composition. The Bottle: The blue and gold cap is a metaphor of the world. The blue is the universal color that unites all of us. It is englobed by a golden ring, stamped with the Giorgio Armani signature, a symbol of a unique path that is illuminated by every encounter along the way. This luxurious fragrance is refillable. It is a talisman that encapsulates all encounters that matter. Product Ingredients:  Alcohol, Parfum/Fragrance, Aqua/Water, Linalool, Benzyl Salicylate, Benzyl Alcohol, Hydroxycitronellal, Limonene, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Methyl Anthranilate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol, Citronellol, Eugenol, Citral, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Tris(Tetramethylhydroxypiperidinol) Citrate, Isoeugenol, Cinnamal, Benzyl Benzoate, Ci 17200/Red 33, Ci 60730/Ext. description: My Way Eau de Parfum by Giorgio Armani is the scent of discoveries and connections for an openminded, curious and authentic woman who is ready to broaden her horizons and live meaningful encounters around the world. This feminine fragrance is an encounter of consciously sourced ingredients. The Fragrance: Bergamot meets orange blossom from Egypt in a luminous, sparkling start, with an amplified bright floral bouquet of tuberose and jasmine from India as the beating heart. Finally, a vibrant cedarwood from Virginia meets a sensual vanilla from Madagascar and white musks to sign the composition. The Bottle: The blue and gold cap is a metaphor of the world. The blue is the universal color that unites all of us. It is englobed by a golden ring, stamped with the Giorgio Armani signature, a symbol of a unique path that is illuminated by every encounter along the way. This luxurious fragrance is refillable. It is a talisman that encapsulates all encounters that matter. Product Ingredients:  Alcohol, Parfum/Fragrance, Aqua/Water, Linalool, Benzyl Salicylate, Benzyl Alcohol, Hydroxycitronellal, Limonene, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Methyl Anthranilate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol, Citronellol, Eugenol, Citral, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Tris(Tetramethylhydroxypiperidinol) Citrate, Isoeugenol, Cinnamal, Benzyl Benzoate, Ci 17200/Red 33, Ci 60730/Ext. Violet 2

product_name: Ayala Brut Majeur NV 750ml
description: Open and expressive. Delicate, unveiling notes of citrus, flowers, and white fruits. Balanced, combining freshness and vinosity, precise, fruity, with a long finish. Alcohol:  12%

product_name: Bacardi Reserva Ocho 1L
description: Bacardí 8 Year Old Premium Golden Rum is a refined, carefully-crafted premium rum, famous for its distinctive golden tint and smoothness in taste. 40% Alcohol

product_name: Carolina Herrera Very Good Girl Eau De Parfum 50ml
description:
Fabulous and fearless, Very Good Girl is a bold new interpretation of the iconic Good Girl scent that will walk straight into your heart with its seductive rose scent and red-hot design. Evolving Carolina Herrera's vision of the duality of the modern woman, this sumptuous and surprising Eau de Parfum shows us that the multifaceted nature of contemporary femininity is where the true beauty of being a woman lies.  
 
 Ingredients:  ALCOHOL DENAT., PARFUM (FRAGRANCE), AQUA (WATER), LINALOOL, LIMONENE, COUMARIN, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, CITRAL, ISOEUGENOL, GERANIOL, CI 14700 (RED 4), CI 60730 (EXT. VIOLET 2).

product_name: Bacardi Cuatro 1L
description: It takes four years maturing in a barrel under the Caribbean sun to create the unique taste of BACARDÍ Añejo Cuatro. It's time well spent. Just like those special moments shared with friends enjoying Añejo Cuatro. 40% Alcohol

product_name: Bacardi Carta Blanca 1L 37.5%
description: Bacardí Carta Blanca White Rum was first created by Don Facundo Bacardí Masso in 1862 and has since been recognised as the world's most-awarded rum. Alcohol: 37.5%

product_name: Baileys Original Irish Cream Liqueur 200ml
description: Baileys is the most popular Irish Cream Liqueur around the globe and has been awarded more medals at the San Francisco World Spirits Competition than any of its competitors. With its distinct velvety texture, it is a perfect combination of smooth cream and whiskey. Enjoy on its own, over ice or in your favourite coffee. And if you are looking for more ways to indulge, from gooey Baileys Irish Cream Cheesecake to classy Baileys Espresso Martini, Baileys recipes hit the sweet spot every time. Drawing on Irish traditions in dairy and distilling, the unique combination took four years to perfect the ultimate liquid treat.

product_name: Baileys Original Irish Cream Liqueur 1L
description: Baileys is the most popular Irish Cream Liqueur around the globe and has been awarded more medals at the San Francisco World Spirits Competition than any of its competitors. With its distinct velvety texture, it is a perfect combination of smooth cream and whiskey. Enjoy on its own, over ice or in your favourite coffee. And if you are looking for more ways to indulge, from gooey Baileys Irish Cream Cheesecake to classy Baileys Espresso Martini, Baileys recipes hit the sweet spot every time. Drawing on Irish traditions in dairy and distilling, the unique combination took four years to perfect the ultimate liquid treat.

product_name: Baileys Salted Caramel Liqueur 1L
description: Take a swirl on the sweet side with a scrumptious salted caramel liqueur. We’ve blended the smooth taste of caramel with velvety Baileys Original Irish Cream, a pinch of salt and other flavours and ingredients to produce this delicious liqueur. A drop or two makes Baileys desserts and cakes sing, or if you’re not in the mood for dessert, simply pour over ice, sit down and enjoy. Who need rules when you’ve got Baileys Salted Caramel?

product_name: Baileys Tiramisu Liqueur 700ml
description: Baileys Tiramisu is a cocktail-inspired limited-edition liqueur combining the deliciousness of Baileys Irish Cream with the decadent flavours of a tiramisu dessert. Alcohol:  17%

product_name: Baileys Original Irish Cream Liqueur 2 x 1L Twin Pack
description: Baileys is the most popular Irish Cream Liqueur around the globe and has been awarded more medals at the San Francisco World Spirits Competition than any of its competitors. With its distinct velvety texture, it is a perfect combination of smooth cream and whiskey. Enjoy on its own, over ice or in your favourite coffee. And if you are looking for more ways to indulge, from gooey Baileys Irish Cream Cheesecake to classy Baileys Espresso Martini, Baileys recipes hit the sweet spot every time. Drawing on Irish traditions in dairy and distilling, the unique combination took four years to perfect the ultimate liquid treat.

product_name: Baileys Espresso Creme Liqueur 1L
description: A delicious combination that was meant to be. Real Colombian coffee and other natural flavours meet yummy Baileys Original Irish Cream for a big bold hit of wonderful. Perfect for when you need to concentrate on the important things in life: coffee, chocolate and creamy Baileys. Enjoy neat, in one of our indulgent coffee cocktail recipes, or splash into coffee and hot drinks for an extra shot of wow. Tasting notes:Coffee, cream and a hint of cocoa

product_name: Bird In Hand Sauvignon Blanc 750ml
description: This pure, handpicked sauvignon blanc by adelaide hills award winning winery, bird in hand displays sensational citrus, honey and tropical flavors, minerality, elegance and has a fresh and vibrant finish. 60% sauvignon blanc grapes, balanced with 40%, the resulting blend has lifted varietal aromas and flavors of passion fruit, lemon zest and gooseberry with hints of freshly cut grass. on the palate, it is light- bodied, vibrant and zippy with refreshing acidity and a clean finish.

product_name: Chalk Hill Alpha Crucis Blewett Springs Grenache 750ml
description: Highly aromatic, with rose petals, pomegranate, dark cherry, plum and licorice notes on the nose. A medium bodied Grenache that has classic characters of dark cherry and pomegranate, with florals and layers of lingering spice. A delightful wine with great pedigree. Whilst beautiful in its youth, it will age gracefully for the next 8 years. FOOD MATCH: Roast quail with crispy bacon, peas and mint. Alcohol:  14%

product_name: Absolut Vodka Sweden Lime 1L
description: Absolut Lime is made exclusively from natural ingredients, and unlike some other flavored vodkas, it doesn’t contain any added sugar. To put it short and simple: Absolut Lime is smooth, rich and very fresh with a distinct note of freshly pressed lime and a slightly sweet and fruity finish. Alcohol: 40% Color: Clear Nose: Very fresh with distinct notes of freshly pressed limes followed by a touch of complex fruitiness and peels of lime Taste: Smooth, rich and fresh with a deep fruitiness, a slight acidity and a natural sweetness. Long, smooth and fruity finish!

product_name: Absolut Vodka Sweden Original 1L
description: Absolut Vodka is a Swedish vodka made exclusively from natural ingredients, and unlike some other vodkas, it doesn’t contain any added sugar. In fact Absolut is as clean as vodka can be. Still, it has a certain taste: Rich, full-bodied and complex, yet smooth and mellow with a distinct character of grain, followed by a hint of dried fruit. Color: Clear Taste: Rich, full-bodied and complex, yet smooth and mellow with a distinct character of grain, followed by a hint of dried fruit. Alcohol: 40%

product_name: Absolut Vodka Original 200ml Bottle
description: Absolut Vodka is a Swedish vodka made exclusively from natural ingredients, and unlike some other vodkas, it doesn’t contain any added sugar. In fact Absolut is as clean as vodka can be. Still, it has a certain taste: Rich, full-bodied and complex, yet smooth and mellow with a distinct character of grain, followed by a hint of dried fruit. Color: Clear Taste: Rich, full-bodied and complex, yet smooth and mellow with a distinct character of grain, followed by a hint of dried fruit.

product_name: 1800 Tequila Coconut 200ml
description: Smooth and medium bodied tequila with notes of Coconut.   Named in commemoration of the year in which the first expertly crafted tequila was unveiled, 1800 tequila still follows the standards of the original formula, created in the year 1975. 1800 Coconut is created by infusing Jose Cuervo's signature 100% Agave double-distilled 1800 Silver Tequila with natural, ripe Coconut flavour. With its slightly-sweet and medium bodied tropical taste, this versatile spirit is delicious on the rocks and tastes great mixed with pineapple juice.     Crystal clear colour with blonde highlights   Tasting notes - nose: soft and tropical with sweet Agave   Tasting notes - palate: smooth and medium bodied with notes of Coconut   Tasting notes - finish: long, subtle sweet Coconut in the finish   ABV 35%

product_name: Zacapa Solera Gran Reserva 700ml
description:
Zacapa Solera Gran Reserva is a a complex and full-bodied dark rum. Aged in ex-American Whiskey and ex-Sherry casks to deliver flavour notes of raisined fruit, Zacapa Solera Gran Reserva can be enjoyed neat, on the rocks or to give classic cocktails  like an Old-Fashioned a delicious twist.  Tasting notes:It has a sweet honeyed viscosity more reminiscent of a liqueur than an aged spirit; a great depth of raisined fruit and apricot preserves, building to an intense heart of savoury oak, nutmeg, with notes of coffee and delicately sweet vanilla, balanced with a spicy touch of cinnamon and ginger on the pleasantly astringent finish; truly a rum for the discerning
palate.

product_name: 1800 Tequila Coconut 700ml
description: Jose Cuervo's signature double-distilled 1800® Silver Tequila infused with natural, ripe coconut flavor. With its slightly-sweet and medium-bodied tropical taste, this versatile spirit is delicious on the rocks and also tastes great mixed with pineapple juice. Alcohol:  35%

product_name: Wynns The Banker Coonawarra Cabernet Sauvignon 750ml
description: A densely coloured wine with a vivid purple hue. a diverse array of blackberry, dark cherry and black olive, further complexed by notes of liquorice, violets and tobacco. classy oak contributes cigarbox nuances. the rich dark and smooth palate is filled with blackberry and black olive. classic supple, powdery tannins and balanced acidity, frame the dense core of fruit creating a beautifully balanced wine. refined french oak supports the pristine fruit ensuring the wine finishes with poise, balance and seamless length

product_name: Wynns Black Label Cabernet Sauvignon 750ml
description: First produced in 1954 as wynns coonawarra estate cabernet sauvignon, ‘black label’ has established a reputation for displaying excellent varietal and regional characteristics. produced from only the top 20-25% of cabernet fruit available from wynns coonawarra estate, this wine has style and stature. a perennial favourite in auction circles, this wine is one of australia’s most collectable wines and a benchmark cabernet sauvignon which consistently delivers potential for medium to long-term cellaring. wild berries, black olive and rhubarb notes lead. fragrant nutmeg and cedary oak is underpinned by delicate notes of sage and violet florals. dark cassis stretches the length of the palate. fine, powdery tannins and succulent acidity support rich fruit with exceptional poise.

product_name: Wynns John Riddoch 750ml
description: First made in 1982, the john riddoch cabernet sauvignon was conceived as a flagship wine for wynns. john riddoch himself was a true visionary. amongst his many achievements are the building of the wynns gabled winery and the establishment of the coonawarra fruit colony. this wine is made in small quantities from the best available fruit grown on the estate’s extensive cabernet plantings. it has become a definitive coonawarra cabernet sauvignon, made only in years when grapes of extraordinarily high quality are available, using less than one per cent of the top cabernet grapes. concentrated, intricate aromatics of opulent black fruits, fine cedary french oak and complex aromatics, merging with notes of olive and cassis. majestic palate, filled with defined and concentrated flavours of cassis and olive, underpinned by delicate perfumed spice, cedar notes. firm, chalky tannin, vibrant acidity enhance the structure and texture.

product_name: Wild Turkey American Honey 1L
description: The only bourbon-based liqueur on the market, Wild Turkey liqueur brings out the best flavours of premium bourbon, but with real honey to give it a sweetness that's hard to resist. The palate is a bit like syrup and glides around the mouth with obvious notes of vanilla and citrus. Perfectly suited for after-dinner consumption, it rounds-out Wild Turkey's portfolio of exceptional products. Wild Turkey Liqueur also marries well with Wild Turkey Bourbon to make a Kentucky-style Golden Nail. It also goes well with vanilla ice cream, pecan pie, or as an ingredient in a butterscotch sauce. Alcohol:  35.5%

product_name: Wild Turkey 81 Proof 1L
description: An 81 Proof bourbon crafted by Wild Turkey associate distiller Eddie Russell son of master distiller Jimmy. Palate: Rich and thick, notes of caramel, manuka honey and fudge, hints of rhubarb and custard sweets and oily espresso beans. Finish: Caramel and coffee, hints of Black Forest honey and Hot Cross Buns. Charred and spicy.  Alcohol: 40.5%.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Spicebomb Eau De Toilette 90ml
description: The bottle of the fragrance Spicebomb is a real luxury object: after being fashioned like a diamond for Flowerbomb, the grenade is reinvented in a glass sculpture with chased, even and masculine facets. The ultimate detail: the fragrance is released by priming the pin, which has been revisited with the Viktor&Rolf seal. The olfactory explosion is inescapable.

product_name: Valentino Valentina Edp 50ml
description: The ingredients that define the femininity and uniqueness of the valentino woman have inspired a new perfume called valentina. with attitude, sophistication and unexpected characteristics, the bouquet of valentina blends an irreverent italian floral oriental.

product_name: Valentino Donna Born In Roma Green Stravaganza Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: As the sun rises and shines over the eternal city, Born in Roma Green Stravaganza takes you on a bold adventure to the cool gardens of Roma where you are free to live and express your unique ways.  Born from the abundant gardens of Roma, this floral-ambery woody fragrance opens the door to an extravagant world created by distinctive lapsang souchong tea accord and radiant jasmine absolute with a captivating touch from vanilla extract. Born in Roma Green Stravaganza leads a way into the extravagance of Roma, allowing cool kids to feel the energy, unleash their personalities, and live excessively, because there are many vibrant ways to be you. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: Opening with a smoky tea leaves scent, this fragrance draws you into a sensual garden with Lapsang Souchong tea accord. Heart Note: Delicate jasmine absolute illuminates the heart of the mix with its solar and floral facets, unveiling modern feminity of this note. Base Note: Sweet yet smoky drops of vanilla extract add a bewitching touch to this sensual journey, pushing the extravagance to extremes.

product_name: Black Bottle Xo Brandy 700ml
description: Eighteen-year-old double pot distilled spirit forms the remarkable foundation of this uniquely Australian XO. Meticulously chosen parcels of up to 40-year-old double pot brandy are blended in to add sumptuous depth and complexity.Palate: Aged toasty oak and raisin with gentle hints of fig, cinnamon and hazelnut Mix With: Savour Black Bottle XO neat Alcohol: 39.1%

product_name: Clinique Anti-Blemish Solutions Clinical Clearing Gel 30ml
description: Results As Good As A Leading Topical Prescription In Clearing Blemishes. Our Daily Treatment Gel Starts Clearing Blemishes Upon Application. Helps Prevent New Ones From Making An Unwelcome Appearance. Make Visibly Clearer Skin A Way Of Life. 30ml / 1 Fl. Oz.

product_name: Bacardi Carta Oro Rum 1L
description: BACARDÍ Gold Rum is hand blended, charcoal filtered and aged for two years in American white oak barrels. The liquid brings depth and character to classic rum cocktails, while maintaining a smooth finish. 40% Alcohol

product_name: Valentino Donna Born In Roma Coral Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: With Born in Roma Coral Fantasy, Valentino invites you to a new Rome at sunset. As coral light floods the skyline, it’s time for a new expression of fantasy: inspired by the cultural magnificence of Rome, in a moment of your own making. Born in Roma Donna Coral Fantasy is a floral fruity scent energized by a colorful pink gold kiwi accord. Blended with feminine Rose Accords and Jasmin Grandiflorum, this fragrance reveals a bright contemporary femininity Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: Floral and fruity, built through the association of energetic orange, feminine rose and an aerial Jasmin grandiflorum, creating the feeling of lightness, with a scent. Heart Note: The rose accord brings unmatched femininity into the mix.The luminous and silky aroma softens the notes, blooming like an incomparable bouquet. Base Note: A unique signature thanks to the warmth and softness of Musks note combined with the edginess of Ambrette Seeds absolute accord.

product_name: VOK Advokaat Liqueur 500ml
description: Advokaat Liqueur is a blend of fresh eggs, cane sugar mellow brandy with a hint of vanilla – the perfect smooth and creamy blend. Alcohol:  17%

product_name: Valentino Uomo Born In Roma Yellow Dream Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: With Born in Roma Yellow Dream, Valentino opens a new chapter for a world that needs to dream. The color of Rome, bathed in yellow light, to inspires dreams of tomorrow, new beginnings for now. Signed by the depth and warmth of Rome’s light, Born in Roma Uomo Yellow Dream is a spicy oriental fragrance, built around a tension of comfort and floral notes. It is given an unexpected, generous addiction with a sensual vanilla accord. Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: Spicy with a hint of freshness, the cinnamon in this scent compliments the sweet and comforting aroma it holds. Heart Note: Lavandin creates a blooming sense of freshness. The aromatic and floral notes give a refreshing texture to the scent, bringing a level of timeless yet familiar refinement. Base Note: Evolving into a warm and woody scent, the vanilla adds a wholesome and rich touch to finalize the bouquet created by this fragrance.

product_name: YSL Black Opium Eau de Parfum 90ml
description:
An Edible Floral Oriental Fragrance Top Notes - Par accord, Mandarin essence Middle Notes - Orange blossum asbolute, Jasmine absolute Base Notes - Black coffee accord, Vanilla absolute, Patchouli 
 The Inspiration: 
 Black Opium Eau de Parfum is a modern glam rock version of a classic feminine scent. Designed like a shot of adrenalin, this fragrance will stop them intensely in their tracks. 
 The Personality: 
 Assertive and unique, the Black Opium woman embodies the new Yves Saint Laurent spirit. Free and self-confident, she expresses a femininity glamourous yet impertinent. Always searching for new experiences, nothing will stop her.

product_name: YSL Black Opium Eau de Parfum 50ml

product_name: YSL Libre Eau de Parfum 30ml
description: The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme, to live everything to excess Libre: Women's Fragrance of Freedom LIBRE Eau De Parfum, the new women’s floral fragrance by Yves Saint Laurent, represents the freedom to live everything to excess. Your boundless creativity, your complete emancipation, your ever-evolving femininity. Libre, the French word for ‘free’, pays tribute to YSL’s most defining value: Freedom. The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme. A statement women’s fragrance for those who lives by her own rules. Fragrance Scent The first floral lavender. The tension between the burning sensuality of orange blossom from Morocco, the boldness of lavender from France and a daring note of Musk Accord with a feminine twist. A singular trail like a breath of freedom. Fragrance Bottle A couture, sharp-angled bottle that is dually architecturally masculine and sensually feminine. The iconic Libre it-bottle reflects a tension between masculinity and femininity, like a straight geometric silhouette embedded in the smoking jacket. The iconic YSL Cassandre – an oversized luxury accessory – is strikingly bent and nailed into the glass like a jewel. Sexy golden chains and an asymmetric black lacquered cap adorn the bottle to complete it as a manifesto of freedom and irreverence.

product_name: YSL Libre Eau de Parfum 90ml
description: The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme, to live everything to excess Libre: Women's Fragrance of Freedom LIBRE Eau De Parfum, the new women’s floral fragrance by Yves Saint Laurent, represents the freedom to live everything to excess. product_name: Valentino Donna Born In Roma Yellow Dream Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: With Born in Roma Yellow Dream, Valentino opens a new chapter for a world that needs to dream. The color of Rome, the eternal city bathed in yellow light, inspires dreams of tomorrow, new beginnings for now. Born from the dream of Rome, bathing in a golden light, this floral perfume, created from the scent of a thousand rose petals is reinforced by the contrasting scent of musks. A scent full of optimism and energy. Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: The delicacy of a peony accord captured in a scent. Like the flower, the fragrance’s petals peel one by one, offering a fresh and airy aroma at the top of this note. Heart Note: An airy bouquet blooms at the heart of this fragrance. Led by a delicate Turkish rose essence, obtained by re injecting rose water into a solid form revealing the flower’s fresh green facets, together with its silky, opulent trail. Base Note: This floral heart is soothed by the reassuring, comforting notes of a pure accord. Then in total contrast, the dry down is teased by the power of white musk a sensual white musk overdose that develops into a lingering powdery softness.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Spicebomb Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: The bottle of the fragrance spicebomb is a real luxury object: after being fashioned like a diamond for flowerbomb, the grenade is reinvented in a glass sculpture with chased, even and masculine facets. the ultimate detail: the fragrance is released by priming the pin, which has been revisited with the viktor&rolf seal. the olfactory explosion is inescapable.

product_name: Valentino Voce Viva Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: The sound of your voice, the scent of your fragrance, both a magnetic presence. Voce Viva celebrates every woman’s unique voice in one declaration: My voice, My strength. An invitation to voice dreams, and to live them. Voce Viva, a living voice. A floral reimagining in the spirit of Valentino’s contemporary femininity - couture Orange Blossom absolute and golden Gardenia accord paired with colorful Italian Bergamot and Mandarin. This harmony is made unexpectedly addictive through a surprising layer, a traditionally masculine accord of Crystal Moss with an infusion of Vanilla. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: A colorful and sparkling opening of Italian Bergamot is softened by sweet and juicy mandarin. Heart Note: An opulent bouquet of Orange Blossom absolute is refreshed with a Golden Gardenia accord. Base Note: An unexpected Crystal Moss brings a modern intensity to the base, becoming wholly addictive by the addition of an enveloping vanilla infusion.

product_name: Clinique Chubby Stick Moisturizing Lip Colour Balm
description: Super-Nourishing Balm Is Loaded With Mango And Shea Butters. Just What Dry, Delicate Lips Need To Feel Comfortably Soft And Smooth. Twelve Natural-Looking Lip Tints In All, Each With A Subtle Sheen.

product_name: Valentino Donna Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Designed for living life in elegant irreverence, Valentino Donna is full of life, and romantic. Inspired by Rome, where past and present coexist, it tells a story of independent passion. A timeless floral scent, created around the distinct couture elegance of opulent Iris notes, Donna Eau De Parfum juxtaposes the flower’s powdery femininity with the mysterious sensuality of Turkish Rose accords, modernized with a touch of Patchouli. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: The opulence of Turkish rose is one like no other. It brings a light to the bouquet, redefining femininity and reframing the softness of a silky scent. Heart Note: Iris’s sophistication complexifies the fragrance, with an elegant twist and a powdery element. Base Note: At the base, patchouli’s woody and earthy notes deepen the bouquet into a powerful chypre scent, tying the fragrance together.

product_name: Valentino Voce Viva Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: The sound of your voice, the scent of your fragrance, both a magnetic presence. Voce Viva celebrates every woman’s unique voice in one declaration: My voice, My strength. An invitation to voice dreams, and to live them. Voce Viva, a living voice. A floral reimagining in the spirit of Valentino’s contemporary femininity - couture Orange Blossom absolute and golden Gardenia accord paired with colorful Italian Bergamot and Mandarin. This harmony is made unexpectedly addictive through a surprising layer, a traditionally masculine accord of Crystal Moss with an infusion of Vanilla. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: A colorful and sparkling opening of Italian Bergamot is softened by sweet and juicy mandarin. Heart Note: An opulent bouquet of Orange Blossom absolute is refreshed with a Golden Gardenia accord. Base Note: An unexpected Crystal Moss brings a modern intensity to the base, becoming wholly addictive by the addition of an enveloping vanilla infusion.

product_name: Valentino Uomo Born In Roma Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: Inspired by Rome, a place where past and present coexist, Born in Roma fragrances tell a story of self-expression. A celebration of people living life freely, while embracing their heritage by twisting the classic with the unexpected into new fragrance statements.  Born in Roma Uomo is a woody vetiver aromatic fragrance. A cool vibrating facet of mineral salt and spicy ginger twists the classic signature of aromatic sage and smoked vetiver. Born in Roma Uomo is a statement of personality. Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: An unconventional ingredient for a masculine fragrance provides a floral twist of freshness. Heart Note: A blend of aromatic sage bring a powerful, earthy scent to the heart of the fragrance, for a sense of timeless elegance. Base Note: Smoked vetiver ties the fragrance together with smoky texture.

product_name: Veuve Clicquot Yellow Label Brut 750ml
description: The quintessential Yellow Label - famous the world over. Medium bodied with a fine bead. Citrus, light toast and soft brioche flavours.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Flowerbomb Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: This fragrance is a more sensual, more Oriental version of the Eau De Parfum Flowerbomb. More concentrated, hence more glamorous and chic. Scent starts with bergamot, sambac jasmine. Comes the heart with osmanthus, white flowers, balms. Dry down unveils patchouli, amber, benzoin, vanilla.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Ruby Orchid Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: Flowerbomb Ruby Orchid by Viktor&Rolf is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. Flowerbomb Ruby Orchid was launched in 2021.  Top notes are Peach and Vine; middle note is Orchid; base note is Vanilla Bean.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Flowerbomb Dew Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Flowerbomb Dew is the new second skin floral facet of Viktor & Rolf's Flowerbomb perfume: dewy and delicate, this Eau de Parfum makes you reconnect with the essential, and gives you the power to reveal your natural glow, with a pure and transparent sensuality.  Flowerbomb Dew is a floriental musky perfume for women, an olfactory bomb of fresh flowers designed around a Dewy Rose Accord. This rose growing in water is infused with transparent morning dew, for a scent that melts on your skin. Envelop yourself with comforting musks, and sensual iris to create the most glowy, second skin floral sensation. A long lasting perfume for women, sensual and second skin, dewy and delicate. The new scent is encapsulated in a slightly transparent pearly white bottle, a new gem in the Flowerbomb family by Viktor & Rolf, inviting women to get rid of all the unnecessary, to reveal their power. Directions: Apply on pulse points: wrist, inner elbow and neck. Product Ingredients:  CODE FIL : B242799/1 ALCOHOL, PARFUM / FRAGRANCE, AQUA / WATER, LINALOOL, LIMONENE, BENZYL SALICYLATE, BENZYL ALCOHOL, CITRONELLOL, COUMARIN, ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, METHYL ANTHRANILATE, CITRAL, GERANIOL, CI 60730 / EXT. VIOLET 2, CI 14700 / RED 4.

product_name: Wolf Blass Black Label Cabernet Shiraz 750ml 15%
description: The elite parcels of shiraz and cabernet sauvignon selected for wolf blass black label are brought together to form a perfect storm of concentrated power. this wine is the darling of collectors as a result, and it should be yours with its magnificent ability to be a rich and concentrated when young and a wonderfully balanced amalgam of flavours with a touch of bottle age. sublime!

product_name: Wolf Blass Grey Cabernet Shiraz 750ml 15%
description: Wolf blass grey label langhorne creek cabernet shiraz is a red wine of distinction, elegance and power, with a dark fruit profile of black cherry and cassis, subtle mineral notes, savoury oak, and finely textured tannins. cabernet shiraz blends pair well with grilled, roast and barbecued red meats, rich braises, and mature cheeses. grey label cabernet shiraz is great with barbecued quail with fennel and thyme, or roast leg of lamb with rosemary and mint.

product_name: Wild Turkey 101 Proof 8Yo 1L
description: Smooth and richly colored, Wild Turkey Straight Kentucky Bourbon Whiskey is a genuine super-premium bourbon carefully crafted in the heart of Kentucky. Wild Turkey 8 Year-Old offers a lesson in traditional American values, most notably, the refusal to compromise on standards of excellence. Wild Turkey 8 Year-Old has an exceptionally soft, but rich aroma for a high proof bourbon, due to quality at all stages of making and aging for 8 years. Its taste is powerful and rich with caramel, vanilla and notes of honey and brown sugar. The finish is very long, rich and full-bodied, powerful, yet soothing.  Alcohol:  50.5%

product_name: Wolf Lane Tropical Gin 700ml
description: New here? Meet our Tropical Gin.  The one that started us on our gin journey, Wolf Lane Tropical Gin brings together thirteen botanicals that are both steeped and vapour-infused to create a taste of the tropics. We use some of the usual suspects: juniper, angelica, cinnamon, cardamom with the addition of native lemon myrtle, pepper-berry, and macadamia. But we think it’s the vapour-infusion of fresh local ruby grapefruits, mangoes and finger limes that set our Tropical Gin apart. Making it a well-balanced, citrus-forward summer gin that will always have a special place in our hearts… and our glass.  Perfect served with soda and a slice of ruby grapefruit, our Tropical Gin is also a welcome addition to any classic gin cocktail. Alcohol:  42.5%

product_name: Wolf Lane Grapefruit Aperitif 700ml
description: Prepare to fall in love with our Grapefruit Aperitif!  Leaving behind the bitterness of traditional aperitifs, we've captured the fresh, fruity and citrus profile of ruby grapefruits to bring you the perfect addition to summer drinking.  We source our fresh fruits and botanicals from the tablelands and FNQ surroundings, including pepper, lemon myrtle, lemon aspen, lillipilli… Served over ice, with soda or in your favourite spritz cocktail, tropical holiday vibes will be coming your way! Alcohol:  20%

product_name: Wolf Lane Davidson Plum Gin 700ml
description: Here at Wolf Lane, we love using native Australian botanicals as much as we love to support our local farmers. So, when the opportunity arose to do both, we jumped at the chance. Wolf Lane Davidson Plum gin is our tropical take on the traditional sloe gin, swapping sloe berries for locally grown Queensland Davidson Plums. A labour of love, we steep the plums for up to three months in our gin, before bottling it at full strength to deliver a truly unique, fruit-forward flavour. We use the entirety of our Davidson Plums in order to harness their intense colour and taste their distinctive flavour. An earthy aroma reminiscing of plum jam and stewed rhubarb with orange notes complements the juniper in this very special creation. Alcohol:  33.2%

product_name: Wolf Lane The Barista Coffee Liqueur 700ml
description: "The Barista'' is the hipster of the Pack. Here in the Tropics, we have access to some of the finest coffee in the country. Our premium coffee liqueur uses pure Australian single origin coffee sourced from Far North Queensland plantations. Bold in flavour with subtle hints of local vanilla and a touch of sweetness.  Wolf Lane’s ‘The Barista Coffee Liqueur’ was born out of a pursuit to create a coffee liqueur that would showcase the quality of coffee we have here in the tropics. Working with local coffee and vanilla growers, we were able to produce a coffee liqueur for the lovers of good coffee.  The Barista Coffee Liqueur delivers a full coffee kick! If you want to make the perfect Espresso Martini, look no further. We also like to keep a bottle chilled to pour over our favourite vanilla ice cream for that late-night pick me up.  Alcohol:  22%

product_name: Wonderful Pistachios Pepper & Garlic Pistachios 168g
description: Ingredients:  Pistachios, salt, pepper, sugar, onion powder, garlic powder, dextrose, lemon juice concentrate, flavor, yeast extract. Storage Conditions:  Store in a cool dry place Warnings:  Contain nuts

product_name: Valentino Uomo Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: Valentino Uomo is a classic Italian style, contemporary and uplifting scent. It’s been refined and crafted with the finest of materials and has a scent of aromatic, smooth and leathery men’s fragrance. The composition opens with bergamot and myrtle, succeeded in the heart by roasted coffee combined with gianduja cream, on a rich base created of cedar and precious leather. INGREDIENTS:  ALCOHOL DENAT., AQUA/WATER/EAU, PARFUM/FRAGRANCE, METHYL CYCLODEXTRIN, ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE, LIMONENE, BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE, LINALOOL, CITRAL, ALCOHOL, TRIS CITRATE, FARNESOL, TETRASODIUM GLUTAMATE DIACETATE, EXT. D&C VIOLET NO. 2 (CI 60730), FD&C BLUE NO. 1 (CI 42090), FD&C RED NO. 4 (CI 14700).

product_name: Ambra Blood Orange Gin 500ml
description: Ambra Blood Orange Gin  showcases our unique process of distilling. Inspired by our Italian heritage, we begin by infusing the peel of local blood oranges, juniper, coriander seeds and licorice root; to then create the small-batch handcrafted Gin you all know and love. Low alcohol and sweetness enables this Gin to be enjoyed neat on ice. Alcohol:  30%

product_name: Ambra Blood Orange Liqueur 500ml
description: Ambra Blood Orange Liqueur (15% alc/vol) is a premium blood orange aperitif inspired by an authentic Italian family recipe passed down through generations. This small batch aperitif handcrafted in Australia with the finest locally-grown Blood Oranges. "From our Hearts to your lips". SERVING SUGGESTION: Serve Ambra Blood Orange as an aperitif mixed as a spritz with Prosecco, soda water or Blood Orange Soda. It is a great addition to cocktails. Alcohol: 15%

product_name: Ambra Limoncello 500ml
description: Limoncello is a premium lemon liqueur inspired by an authentic Italian family recipe passed down through generations. Handcrafted in Australia with the finest locally-grown lemons. "From our Hearts to your lips". SERVING SUGGESTION: Serve Limoncello chilled as an aperitif or mixed as a spritz with Prosecco, tonic water or blood orange soda. Alcohol: 25%

product_name: Ambra Cappuccino Liqueur 500ml
description: Ambra Cappuccino (18% alc/vol) is a premium creamy coffee liqueur inspired by an authentic Italian family recipe passed down through generations. This small batch liqueur is handcrafted in Australia with freshly roasted coffee beans. "From our hearts to your lips". SERVING SUGGESTION: Serve Ambra Cappuccino chilled on ice, add to your favourite cocktail or as an accompaniment to your coffee or sweets. Alcohol: 18%

product_name: Wonderful Pistachios Classic Roasted Salted Almonds 168g
description: Ingredients:  Almonds & salt Storage Conditions:  Store in a cool dry place Warnings:  Contain nuts

product_name: Woodford Reserve Bourbon 1L
description: Woodford Reserve is created at the historic Woodford Reserve Distillery (Labrot & Graham Proprietors) in Woodford County, the smallest and oldest operating distillery in Kentucky, which dates back to 1812. Woodford Reserve is painstakingly hand-crafted, resulting in a whiskey of exceptional depth and character. This medium-bodied Bourbon's nose is sweet and of citrus, tastes of smokey oak, vanilla and cinnamon and finishes long, round and spicy but mellow. Discover for yourself what discerning critics have deemed one of the very best Bourbons on the market. Woodford Reserve is the Official Bourbon of two of horse racing's most important events; The Kentucky Derby and the Breeders' Cup. Every bottle is individually numbered with the batch number and bottle number. 43.2% Alc./Vol.

product_name: Wynns Black Label Shiraz 750ml
description: A superb example of coonawarra’s cool climate style, this wine displays great fruit character, rich and complex flavours of red berries, spice and chocolate with layered fruit underpinned by tightly-focused tannins. dark and focused, filled with juicy and vibrant fruit. blood plum and magnolia pervade the mid palate. sleek, plush tannins frame the bright fruit creating a seamless, layered wine, telling of its cool climate home. 'excellent depth to the colour heralds a wine replete with an abundance of purple and black fruits seamlessly woven together on the medium to full-bodied palate, oak and tannins provide the framework for a wine with a very long life ahead.'

product_name: YSL Libre Eau de Parfum 50ml
description: The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme, to live everything to excess Libre: Women's Fragrance of Freedom LIBRE Eau De Parfum, the new women’s floral fragrance by Yves Saint Laurent, represents the freedom to live everything to excess. Your boundless creativity, your complete emancipation, your ever-evolving femininity. Libre, the French word for ‘free’, pays tribute to YSL’s most defining value: Freedom. The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme. A statement women’s fragrance for those who lives by her own rules. Fragrance Scent The first floral lavender. The tension between the burning sensuality of orange blossom from Morocco, the boldness of lavender from France and a daring note of Musk Accord with a feminine twist. A singular trail like a breath of freedom. Fragrance Bottle A couture, sharp-angled bottle that is dually architecturally masculine and sensually feminine. The iconic Libre it-bottle reflects a tension between masculinity and femininity, like a straight geometric silhouette embedded in the smoking jacket. The iconic YSL Cassandre – an oversized luxury accessory – is strikingly bent and nailed into the glass like a jewel. Sexy golden chains and an asymmetric black lacquered cap adorn the bottle to complete it as a manifesto of freedom and irreverence.

product_name: YSL Y Eau de Parfum 100ml
description: Y Eau De Perfume by Yves Saint Laurent is an aromatic fern perfume for men. it's a new perfume. Y Eau De Perfume was launched in 2018. The nose behind this perfume is dominique ropion. Top notes are bergamot, ginger and apple; Middle notes are sage, juniper berries and geranium; Base notes are vetiver, cedar, amberwood, tonka bean and oliban resin.

product_name: YSL Mon Paris Eau de Parfum 90ml
description: REBEL HEARTS DO DECLARE "JE T'AIME" Passionate love is essential and surrender to it's vertigo is an act of audacity. It can turn Paris upside down. And it is all real for those who dare to live it. That is how Parisian lovers feel. The original MON PARIS Eau de Parfum is a striking "Je t'aime!" declaration. The YSL Parisian femininity, both elegant and dangerous, encapsulated in a head-turning scent. The quintessential gift of love to share. THE SCENT OF PARISIAN BLOOMING LOVE MON PARIS is a modern astounding chypre floral. A vertiginous bouquet of daturas: a mysterious flower that only reveals its precious fragrance at nightfall, one that cannot be extracted. That is why YSL uses a patented technology to capture its olfactive snapshot and reproduce it while preserving nature. Dizzying and intoxicating, the datura is completed with aerial and elegant white peony notes; a delicious red-fruity accent; and a sensual, white patchouli essence, a special bright quality for YSL. Precious white musks finish this modern chypre signature. Hypnotic, simply irresistible. A lasting "Je t'aime!" declaration. THE BOTTLE, THE FIRST SEDUCTION One of the most iconic YSL fragrance bottle designs. A multi-faceted glass falcon both feminine and bold, distinctly modern. Quintessentially cool, the lavallière sits securely around the neck of the Mon Paris bottle is made from soft and matte silk, juxtaposed but two rock leather ties and a stylish shining gold YSL Cassandre. At first constrained by the neck-tie, the Mon Paris lover is overcome by a daring power of seduction, the untying of the bow symbolic of the release that comes with love. A fitting tribute to the Mon Paris woman: an elegant allure and an edgy couture style all of its own. Top Notes:  Strawberry, Raspberry, Bergamot essence, Calone Heart Notes:  Pear flesh, Orange flower absolute, Jasmin Sambac absolute, White Peony, Datura Base Notes:  Patchouli essence, White Musk, Ambrox, Cedarwood essence, Cristal Moss Olfactory Family:  White Chypre
